<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulaic<unclear>e</unclear>karatevaṟku yāṇ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṭu <num value="13"><g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num>- vati netir <num value="14"><g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu tulānāyaṟṟu <hi rend="grantha">pūrvvapakṣa</hi> ttu <hi rend="grantha">Aśva</hi> ti nāḷ tiruma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>laināṭṭut tirukkoṭuṅkuṉṟattu Uṭaiyār tirukkoṭuṅkuṉṟamuṭai
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ya nāyanāṟkut tirununtāviḷak kerivatākak kaḷakkuṭināṭṭuk kaḷakkuṭiyā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉa kara<unclear>van</unclear>tapurattup piḷḷaiyār Aḻakapperumāḷ Akapparivārattu Ula
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaḷantāṉ Aḻakapperumāḷāṉa Avaṉinārāyaṇatevaṉ Iṭṭa viḷakku ne
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ytāṅki Iraṇṭu pātamoṉṟu muḷḷa cervaippittaḷait tirukkuttuviḷak
<lb n="8"/>koṉṟiṉāl Iṭai Iraṇṭe Eṇpatiṉ palam cantirātittavaṟ celva
<lb n="9" break="no"/>tākat tirunu <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>paṉ<hi rend="grantha">mā he</hi><note n="225-1">The latter portion of lines 9 and 10 appear to have been left unengraved.</note> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> 
</p>

